NPCName "Waster"
Location "City on the Coast"
Description ""
Unknown_Desc "a sick looking guy, he looks a bit scared too."
Known_Desc "One of the wasters. He looks very nervous and is mumbling something about demons."
Detailed_Desc "a man with a dirty old robe on him, everytime he sees movement near him, he gets shocked. Something is REALLY wrong about this guy."
/* Float message nodes */

Floatnode "floater1"
notes ""
{
"The demons are approaching...",
"Hide while you still can.",
"I'm scared.",
"Please, get them away from me!",
"They're everywhere!"
}

